TITLE: CSS map - C17 Train Canal map
AUTHOR: Sota Poika
E-MAIL: omg91@hotmail.com.com
WEBSITE: -

FILENAME: he_c17_train_canal.bsp
FILESIZE: 2.464 mb
DATE RELEASED: 18 april 2007

CREDITS: -

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS: Extract cstrike -folder to X:\Program Files\Valve\Steam\SteamApps\<Your Steam Account>\counter-strike source (Where the "X" is your drive)

DESCRIPTION: Here's my first HE_ map and it turned out better than I tought myself.. It features:

- Moving trains

- Working grenade spawning machine, 1 for each side

- Kinda detailed 3D skybox

- City17 feel, I tried to make it as close as I could.

Map is for 5 vs.5 because it's enough for this map. Trains are dangerous, so watchout! I maybe support HDR later, not now. This map was supposed to be 2-3 hours map but I wanted to make it detailed
and all so it took 4 days, every day I worked 1.5h.

BUGS: -

COMMENTS: This is re-added, nothing else..
